To download executable to QNX:
- Connect to the board using eval_con
- TFTP download QNX image (/tftpboot/dechen/ifs-palmbeach-eval-rommon.bin)
- run "ifconfig -a" to find out IP address (inet)
- rlogin to dechen-ultra5
- run /opt/QNXsdk/host/solaris/sparc/usr/bin/ntoppc-gdb (aliased as qnx_gdb)
- (gdb) target qnx <ip>:8000
- (gdb) upload <host filename> <qnx filename>
- (gdb) download <qnx filename> <host filename>

